Dominos has gotten really good in the last few years.
You're saying, "Five stars?
For Dominos?
C'mon.
"   No, you come on.
Their pizza's good, it's fast, it's affordable, and their customer service is spectacular.
Is it Spinato's or NYPD?
No, but Spinato's not open late, they're way more expensive, and they don't have an awesome online ordering system.
For economy pizza delivery, it's basically the Hut vs Dominos vs Papa John's.
Out of those three, my favorite is the big D.

