This is my go-to place for dinner when I'm pressed for time or just don't really feel like cooking.
My family really likes their garlic sauce to dip their pizza in.
The downside is that each sauce is .75 cents each.
They deliver!
That saves me so much time, there is a two dollar charge for that.
